Module biblioteka

Class Leidinys

java.lang.Object
biblioteka.core.Leidinys
All Implemented Interfaces:
Borrowable, Postponable, Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Knyga, Zurnalas
public abstract class Leidinys extends Object implements Postponable, Serializable
Represents a generic publication or item in the library. This abstract class provides common properties and functionalities for all types of library items, such as title, publication year, and page count. Subclasses like Knyga (Book) or Zurnalas (Magazine) will extend this class to add specific attributes.
